  "analysis": "Only python3 is confirmed at /app; ffmpeg/ffprobe/tesseract are not in PATH. To extract Zork moves from the video, we need either installed tools or Python libraries. Next we should check apt/pip availability and installed Python modules before deciding whether to install ffmpeg/tesseract or use existing libraries.",
